price increase of 5% to 12% on medical packaging styles of Tyvek® effective
September 1, 2011.  This pricing will be
effective through December, 2012 barring any significant event impacting the
healthcare packaging industry.
Your account manager will be
sending an updated price list containing 2011 pricing information by style
number to you shortly. 

 

We place high value on our
